{"tid":2167370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你仲戒緊黨鐵嗎？","createTime":"2020-08-21T05:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T12:46:21.000Z","uid":167802,"like":60,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b0a5689925a762fda3ba674a6404eaf9fff8e0","tid":2167370,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:26:42.000Z","msg":"尋日有少少諸事不順<br />\n因工作需要搭巴士遊晒港九新界<br />\n大汗疊細汗 喘晒氣之際<br />\n諗起如果搭黨鐵會舒服好多<br />\n先至驚覺自己原來已經戒鐵戒咗足足一年<br />\n<br />\n每日都會提早起身<br />\n同黨鐵比較每日可能用多咗個幾兩個鐘時間搭車<br />\n練成咗搭車開工大法<br />\n記得有幾次公路嚴重瀨屎，我係會落車行到去唔塞嘅地方轉車<br />\n<br />\n諗番轉頭，一啲都無後悔自己一次都無再搭過黨鐵<br />\n睇住自己身邊嘅人，有好多搭得一次，就忍唔住之後都繼續搭落去<br />\n人變懶係容易過變勤力<br />\n但當我每次諗起<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">7.21</span></span>同<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">8.31</span></span>嘅畫面，我戒鐵嘅決心只會變得更加堅定，無論身邊嘅人點樣改變都好。<br />\n<br />\n幾支竹一扎斷節難<br />\n我至今仍然相信<br />\n每樣最細嘅事只要夠多人做就會力量無窮<br />\n罷睇TVB 罷用八達通 支持黃店 文宣 乜嘢都好<br />\n每日提醒自己 <span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>不進 則退</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你又仲有無堅持戒黨鐵？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一直都戒緊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無戒過/放棄咗"},{"pid":"696d1cdb0442e8c2ffcc85520312a03d6ac4166f","tid":2167370,"uid":80,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:40:16.000Z","msg":"盡量都搭巴士<br />\n<br />\n但班次太<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0e13d3057cca4558294b27e5e7d9445bbd0b16","tid":2167370,"uid":181581,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:44:42.000Z","msg":"冇得揀咪搭囉，有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27adf20970449ce59432820f3f4b26ce018368e7","tid":2167370,"uid":167802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e0e13d3057cca4558294b27e5e7d9445bbd0b16","tid":2167370,"uid":181581,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:44:42.000Z","msg":"冇得揀咪搭囉，有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"無得揀就無辦法啦"},{"pid":"98769740be626f0868cbd76a5a84b37c600127bc","tid":2167370,"uid":277486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"本身都唔多搭鐵，有埋九巴月票更加唔會搭"},{"pid":"698a7e162ecb38c1c18f586c506fab2f317fddb7","tid":2167370,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔多搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為本身好垃圾"},{"pid":"8e86beeef2a202459bc80bc4cfce06fb37810928","tid":2167370,"uid":156376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"有巴士嘅情況下都會盡量搭巴士"},{"pid":"1a2bb47d10a11ffec6ae5e0c2684d8f70fa95763","tid":2167370,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:57:08.000Z","msg":"大西北撚以前一年都唔會搭多過10次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e8b6770d5a823b24862d7e013565c562410b79","tid":2167370,"uid":51761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:58:21.000Z","msg":"我9成搭巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7035a09dae8042f50432b06740c091043be685e4","tid":2167370,"uid":341040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"7成巴士<br />\n<br />\n搭地鐵綠卡/爆閘<p class=\"center\"></p>"},{"pid":"31fc792f5997bdd2b68e09117247b19ee5d416bc","tid":2167370,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:00:55.000Z","msg":"是的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im