e":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:20:07.000Z","msg":"耐冇搭到唔記得搭黨鐵係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938090e5d14c96a87474d86201f9be95915b44af","tid":2167370,"uid":229607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:23:33.000Z","msg":"831 之前無地鐵我會唔識出街, 巴士只識屋企樓下果4條線, 船只會搭去離島用<br />\n<br />\n831 後我而家已經識搭港島9成既巴士線, 8, 8H, 8P, 8X 都識分, 活用巴士+小巴+電車+渡輪 (天星 + 珊瑚海)... 地鐵就算快一倍時間都會揀巴士"},{"pid":"4059e94179ed94f7e24726b09af5f07f1b4b76a1","tid":2167370,"uid":284404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b679773a32fb14ff2337c41e3ce6f81e3e88f1e0","tid":2167370,"uid":297160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:27:32.000Z","msg":"中學開始已經冇再搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又貴又冇位坐又收唔到訊號"},{"pid":"4ce182fc5acacdbf495817d73638b15259ef8353","tid":2167370,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"938090e5d14c96a87474d86201f9be95915b44af","tid":2167370,"uid":229607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:23:33.000Z","msg":"831 之前無地鐵我會唔識出街, 巴士只識屋企樓下果4條線, 船只會搭去離島用<br />\n<br />\n831 後我而家已經識搭港島9成既巴士線, 8, 8H, 8P, 8X 都識分, 活用巴士+小巴+電車+渡輪 (天星 + 珊瑚海)... 地鐵就算快一倍時間都會揀巴士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:27:39.000Z","msg":"ching犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc4bbe68fdb00ddf26499d1ce9da70a44be2a3e","tid":2167370,"uid":147916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}